++Form view++

This view is used to create, view or edit customer type entries.

[Insert screenshot of the form view here]

The form includes the following fields:

- Name: Title of the customer type.
- Description: Optional note describing how or when to use this type.
- Active: Enables or disables the type for use in the Customers app.


++Delete++

Customer types can be deleted only if they are not assigned to any customer.

If in use, they should be deactivated instead to preserve consistency.
